{
  "chapter": 1,
  "chapter_summary": "萧秋水携左丘超然、唐柔、邓玉函三位好友途经秭归，恰逢长江水道天王朱大天王的手下‘三恶’——薛金英、战其力率众在画舫上劫掠。萧秋水等人挺身而出，唐柔以蜀中唐门银针制服众匪，左丘超然以擒拿手制服战其力，邓玉函剑伤薛金英。‘双刀客’符永祥闻讯赶来，削断画舫缆绳欲借长江急流害人。萧秋水飞身救人，铁衣老翁以铁竿顶住画舫，合力将画舫拖上险滩。老翁怒杀薛金英、战其力，道出三恶不除后患无穷。萧秋水等四人在锦江一带人称‘四兄弟’，虽无结拜之名，却有深厚情谊。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_xi_lou",
      "speaker_name": "萧西楼",
      "listener": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "text": "千万不得招惹权力帮，否则打断你的腿。",
      "tone": "严厉告诫",
      "chapter": 1
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "单刀大汉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "咱是‘长江水道天王’朱大天王的人，现在来做笔生意，请各位不要插手，否则格杀勿论。",
      "tone": "粗声威胁",
      "chapter": 1
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "speaker_name": "萧秋水",
      "listener": "char_zuo_qiu_chao_ran",
      "text": "有话快说。",
      "tone": "不耐烦",
      "chapter": 1
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zuo_qiu_chao_ran",
      "speaker_name": "左丘超然",
      "listener": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "text": "你知道‘朱大天王’是谁吗？",
      "tone": "凝肃",
      "chapter": 1
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "speaker_name": "萧秋水",
      "listener": "char_zuo_qiu_chao_ran",
      "text": "猪八戒？",
      "tone": "戏谑",
      "chapter": 1
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zuo_qiu_chao_ran",
      "speaker_name": "左丘超然",
      "listener": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "text": "长江三峡十二连环坞水道上的大盟主，朱老太爷。",
      "tone": "郑重",
      "chapter": 1
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "speaker_name": "萧秋水",
      "listener": "char_zuo_qiu_chao_ran",
      "text": "哦，这倒有听说过。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 1
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zuo_qiu_chao_ran",
      "speaker_name": "左丘超然",
      "listener": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "text": "你知道使双斧和使长枪的是谁吗？",
      "tone": "追问",
      "chapter": 1
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "speaker_name": "萧秋水",
      "listener": "char_zuo_qiu_chao_ran",
      "text": "你少卖关子好不好？",
      "tone": "不耐烦",
      "chapter": 1
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zuo_qiu_chao_ran",
      "speaker_name": "左丘超然",
      "listener": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "text": "使双斧的叫‘紫金斧’薛金英，使长枪的叫‘枪到人亡’战其力，这两人，武功不错，是朱大天王的得力手下。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 1
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zuo_qiu_chao_ran",
      "speaker_name": "左丘超然",
      "listener": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "text": "你要去对付他们，要不要再考虑考虑？",
      "tone": "劝告",
      "chapter": 1
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "speaker_name": "萧秋水",
      "listener": "char_tang_rou",
      "text": "你们呢？",
      "tone": "询问",
      "chapter": 1
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_rou",
      "speaker_name": "唐柔",
      "listener": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "text": "要考虑。",
      "tone": "沉吟",
      "chapter": 1
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "speaker_name": "萧秋水",
      "listener": "char_tang_rou",
      "text": "哦？",
      "tone": "好奇",
      "chapter": 1
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_rou",
      "speaker_name": "唐柔",
      "listener": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "text": "本来是要教训他们的！",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 1
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_deng_yu_han",
      "speaker_name": "邓玉函",
      "listener": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "text": "现在却考虑杀掉他们。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 1
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "speaker_name": "萧秋水",
      "listener": "char_zuo_qiu_chao_ran",
      "text": "你呢？",
      "tone": "询问",
      "chapter": 1
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zuo_qiu_chao_ran",
      "speaker_name": "左丘超然",
      "listener": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "text": "我就是要你们去杀人，不是去教训人而已。",
      "tone": "叹息",
      "chapter": 1
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "speaker_name": "萧秋水",
      "listener": "char_zuo_qiu_chao_ran",
      "text": "你们？",
      "tone": "反问",
      "chapter": 1
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zuo_qiu_chao_ran",
      "speaker_name": "左丘超然",
      "listener": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "text": "不，我们。",
      "tone": "坚定",
      "chapter": 1
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "持刀大汉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "滚下去！",
      "tone": "粗暴",
      "chapter": 1
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_rou",
      "speaker_name": "唐柔",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你们是朱老太爷手下，一定杀过很多人了？",
      "tone": "阴柔",
      "chapter": 1
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "大汉",
      "listener": "char_tang_rou",
      "text": "没一百，也有五十对了。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 1
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "大汉",
      "listener": "char_tang_rou",
      "text": "加上你一个也不嫌多！",
      "tone": "凶狠",
      "chapter": 1
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_rou",
      "speaker_name": "唐柔",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "好。",
      "tone": "冷淡",
      "chapter": 1
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_rou",
      "speaker_name": "唐柔",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "好，就多加两个。",
      "tone": "阴寒",
      "chapter": 1
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "speaker_name": "萧秋水",
      "listener": "char_xue_jin_ying",
      "text": "早。",
      "tone": "轻松",
      "chapter": 1
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhan_qi_li",
      "speaker_name": "战其力",
      "listener": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "text": "你知道我是谁。",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 1
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "speaker_name": "萧秋水",
      "listener": "char_xue_jin_ying",
      "text": "我知道你是薛金英。",
      "tone": "无视",
      "chapter": 1
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhan_qi_li",
      "speaker_name": "战其力",
      "listener": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "text": "我是在跟你说话。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 1
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "speaker_name": "萧秋水",
      "listener": "char_xue_jin_ying",
      "text": "我开始还以为你是个女孩子，好端端的一个粗老汉怎么又是金又是英的呢？",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 1
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhan_qi_li",
      "speaker_name": "战其力",
      "listener": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "text": "臭小子，你嘴里放干净点！",
      "tone": "暴怒",
      "chapter": 1
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "speaker_name": "萧秋水",
      "listener": "char_xue_jin_ying",
      "text": "知道你还有一个朋友叫做战其力的。",
      "tone": "挑衅",
      "chapter": 1
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhan_qi_li",
      "speaker_name": "战其力",
      "listener": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "text": "你再说！",
      "tone": "怒极",
      "chapter": 1
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "speaker_name": "萧秋水",
      "listener": "char_xue_jin_ying",
      "text": "可惜那人很短命，就死在长江水道，秭归镇的一座画舫上。",
      "tone": "冷讽",
      "chapter": 1
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xue_jin_ying",
      "speaker_name": "薛金英",
      "listener": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "text": "他们是来送死的。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 1
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "speaker_name": "萧秋水",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我这位朋友，姓唐名柔，是蜀中唐门的外系嫡亲，‘四川蜀中唐家’，你们总听说过吧？",
      "tone": "介绍",
      "chapter": 1
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "speaker_name": "萧秋水",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "各位不必惊慌，这位唐兄是唐门中少数的暗器不淬毒的子弟之一。",
      "tone": "安抚",
      "chapter": 1
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "speaker_name": "萧秋水",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "他是我的朋友，姓左丘，名超然，为人却一点也不超然，只是有点懒。他是无所不知，胸怀可以装九州十八省进去的人，精通擒拿手，三十六手擒拿，大鹰爪擒拿，小擒拿，奇门擒拿，进步擒拿……什么擒拿他都会。",
      "tone": "自豪介绍",
      "chapter": 1
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zuo_qiu_chao_ran",
      "speaker_name": "左丘超然",
      "listener": "char_zhan_qi_li",
      "text": "这是小天山的缠丝擒拿手，你记住了。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 1
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "speaker_name": "萧秋水",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我还有一位朋友，在外面还没进来，他是海南剑派的高足，姓邓，名玉函，你知道，武林中人都说，不到必要，绝不与海南剑派的人交手，因为他们不出手则已，一出手就是杀手。",
      "tone": "郑重介绍",
      "chapter": 1
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_deng_yu_han",
      "speaker_name": "邓玉函",
      "listener": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "text": "背后说人闲活，不是好人。",
      "tone": "冷峻",
      "chapter": 1
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "speaker_name": "萧秋水",
      "listener": "char_deng_yu_han",
      "text": "邓玉函，难道是好人了？",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 1
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_deng_yu_han",
      "speaker_name": "邓玉函",
      "listener": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "text": "我是好人。",
      "tone": "板脸",
      "chapter": 1
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xue_jin_ying",
      "speaker_name": "薛金英",
      "listener": "char_deng_yu_han",
      "text": "可惜好人都不会长命。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 1
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zuo_qiu_chao_ran",
      "speaker_name": "左丘超然",
      "listener": "char_xue_jin_ying",
      "text": "我们还未向你问话，不准你吵。",
      "tone": "威严",
      "chapter": 1
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zuo_qiu_chao_ran",
      "speaker_name": "左丘超然",
      "listener": "char_xue_jin_ying",
      "text": "你们的头儿，朱大天王在哪里？",
      "tone": "审问",
      "chapter": 1
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "speaker_name": "萧秋水",
      "listener": "char_na_jin_liang",
      "text": "老丈你是干什么呀！",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 1
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_na_jin_liang",
      "speaker_name": "那锦亮",
      "listener": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "text": "老夫要叩谢救命之恩。我辛辛苦苦赚来的半辈子的银子，眼看都被他们劫去了，幸亏你们……",
      "tone": "感激涕零",
      "chapter": 1
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "speaker_name": "萧秋水",
      "listener": "char_na_jin_liang",
      "text": "老丈可是姓那？",
      "tone": "好奇",
      "chapter": 1
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_na_jin_liang",
      "speaker_name": "那锦亮",
      "listener": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "text": "是是是，我是姓那，叫做那锦亮，是杭州人，路经此地……壮士是怎样知道的。",
      "tone": "恭敬",
      "chapter": 1
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "speaker_name": "萧秋水",
      "listener": "char_na_jin_liang",
      "text": "没什么。这姓倒是少得很。",
      "tone": "轻松",
      "chapter": 1
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_na_jin_liang",
      "speaker_name": "那锦亮",
      "listener": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "text": "是是是，壮士等仗义相救，老夫为表谢意，特赠……",
      "tone": "殷勤",
      "chapter": 1
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "speaker_name": "萧秋水",
      "listener": "char_xue_jin_ying",
      "text": "你们头儿下落在哪里，你说出来，我们也不一定杀得了他，说不定反而给他杀了，这样你们也等于报了仇，你们又何苦不说呢！",
      "tone": "劝诱",
      "chapter": 1
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zuo_qiu_chao_ran",
      "speaker_name": "左丘超然",
      "listener": "char_xue_jin_ying",
      "text": "有道是朱大天王是长江黑水道的总瓢把子，手下猛将有‘三英四棍、五剑六掌、双神君’，你和战其力是三英之二，你不说出朱大天王在哪里，只要说出你们的老大‘双刀客’符永祥在哪里便行了。",
      "tone": "冷静分析",
      "chapter": 1
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "speaker_name": "萧秋水",
      "listener": "char_xue_jin_ying",
      "text": "你们三恶是素来行事焦孟不离的，而今符老大在哪里，我想你们也心知肚明吧！",
      "tone": "逼问",
      "chapter": 1
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xue_jin_ying",
      "speaker_name": "薛金英",
      "listener": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "text": "他来了，你们的死期也就到了！",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 1
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "speaker_name": "萧秋水",
      "listener": "char_deng_yu_han",
      "text": "这厮交给你了。",
      "tone": "果断",
      "chapter": 1
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "speaker_name": "萧秋水",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "借用！",
      "tone": "果断",
      "chapter": 1
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zuo_qiu_chao_ran",
      "speaker_name": "左丘超然",
      "listener": "char_tie_yi_lao_weng",
      "text": "好腕力！",
      "tone": "赞叹",
      "chapter": 1
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zuo_qiu_chao_ran",
      "speaker_name": "左丘超然",
      "listener": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "text": "他俩已给我封住了穴道。",
      "tone": "报告",
      "chapter": 1
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "speaker_name": "萧秋水",
      "listener": "char_tie_yi_lao_weng",
      "text": "老丈，您这……",
      "tone": "震惊",
      "chapter": 1
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_yi_lao_weng",
      "speaker_name": "铁衣老翁",
      "listener": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "text": "这种人，还留他在世上干什么？多留一个人渣，多害一群孺子！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 1
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_yi_lao_weng",
      "speaker_name": "铁衣老翁",
      "listener": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "text": "敢情你们是初入江湖，是不是？",
      "tone": "审视",
      "chapter": 1
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "speaker_name": "萧秋水",
      "listener": "char_tie_yi_lao_weng",
      "text": "正是，尚请老前辈多多指点。",
      "tone": "恭敬",
      "chapter": 1
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_yi_lao_weng",
      "speaker_name": "铁衣老翁",
      "listener": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "text": "这批人是朱大天王的手下‘三恶四棍、五剑六掌、双神君’中的‘三恶’，三恶不除，永无宁日，就算你们慈悲为怀，也得为长江两岸的人民想想……就算三恶不除，四棍五剑六掌双神君，也不会放过你们的。",
      "tone": "语重心长",
      "chapter": 1
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zuo_qiu_chao_ran",
      "speaker_name": "左丘超然",
      "listener": "char_tie_yi_lao_weng",
      "text": "前辈说得有理。前辈是——",
      "tone": "恭敬",
      "chapter": 1
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_yi_lao_weng",
      "speaker_name": "铁衣老翁",
      "listener": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "text": "你们之中不是还有一人留在那岸上与符大恶作战吗？我们快赶去瞧瞧！",
      "tone": "急切",
      "chapter": 1
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "speaker_name": "萧秋水",
      "listener": "char_tie_yi_lao_weng",
      "text": "是是。不过以邓玉函的武功，符永祥的双刀定奈不了他的何。",
      "tone": "自信",
      "chapter": 1
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_yi_lao_weng",
